Summary: flew over house from camp penelton marine base into ceanside city airspace, made no sound
divs: Sighting Detailscame over my house from direction of camnp penelton marine base made no noise strobbed on and off flew slow but straight to slow to be plane. came home and saw it at 6 pm on decemeber 4th 2011. ive seen ufos prior this was first time i took pictures. eventually the object just floated away out of sight silently. Having been around ufos before and had many other strange experiences i wasnt afraid of it but i felt the need to get pictures this time and just happened to have my camera in my car, ima keep it in there just in case this thing comes back.
